<H2>SUBSCRIPTION AND PRICING DETAILS</H2><P>
<P>
<P>

<B>Village access:</B> There's two types of information posted at the <i>Traffic Safety Information Village</i> - general information for anyone interested in training and educating drivers, and more detailed information for professionals in the field.  As a subscriber to the Village you receive a password that gives you access to all files posted. You will also receive the hard copy version of the <i>Driver/<b>Education</b></i> &nbspnewsletter by mail. 
<P>
<P>
<B>Full membership:</B> $55 U.S. per year for individuals, $95 U.S. for 
organizations with multiple users ($75 and $128 Canadian for individuals or organizations located in Canada) for full access to the Village database. This fee is fully deductible against the cost of buying space in our Home Page section.<p>

Anyone already subscribing to the hard copy version of the newsletter can deduct the cost of their subscription from the cost of a Village subscription.<P>

<img align="left" src="hot.gif"><STRONG>Subscribe now and become a Village community member. </STRONG>Enquire about becoming a Village sponsor and including your company/organization name, information and logo at the Village site<p>
<HR>

For payment, we suggest you download our <strong><A HREF="form.html">electronic 
form</A></strong>, complete the details, print out the form and send it by Fax or mail. We now accept check, money order, VISA and MASTERCARD. 
<p>
<B>Note:</B> Please do not send credit card numbers over the internet, <br>
since we do not yet have secure transaction technology.<p>
Send to:  

<P><strong>
PDE Publications Inc.<BR>
5334 Yonge St., Suite 310<BR>
Toronto, Ontario, Canada M2N 6M2
<P> 
Tel: (416) 767-4885<BR>
Fax: (416) 767-7425<BR>
