<H2>VILLAGE BOOK STORE</H2><P>

<P> <P> 

<P>To obtain any of these items from PDE Publications, please 
use our convenient <STRONG><A HREF="order.html">ORDER FORM</A></STRONG>. You save on mailing costs by ordering through PDE Publications. <BR>Also, on orders over $100 U.S. ($135 Can) you receive a 10% discount. Shipping and handling charges are $6.00 on the first book and $2.00 on each additional book.<P>

<HR>
<H3>CONTENTS<A NAME="contents"></A></H3>
<UL>
<LI><STRONG><A HREF="#beyond">Beyond Traffic Safety</A></STRONG> by J.P. Rothe

<LI><STRONG><A HREF="#car">Car Accident: A practical recovery manual</A></STRONG> By Jack Smith

