Theory</STRONG> edited by J.P. Rothe

<LI><STRONG><A HREF="#status">Driver Education Status:</A> A National Perspective</STRONG> by Dr. James W. Crowe and Dr. Mohammad R. Torabi

<LI><STRONG><A HREF="#instructional">Instructional support to drivers:</a> The role of in-vehicle feedback in improving driving performance of qualified motorists</STRONG> By  M. J. Kuiken

<LI><STRONG><A HREF="#david">New Driver Car Control:</A> From Kamikaze to Competent</STRONG> by David Thornhill Thompson

<LI><STRONG><A HREF="#truckers">The Trucker's World:</A> Risk, Safety and Mobility</STRONG> by J.P. Rothe

<LI><STRONG><A HREF="#elderly">The Safety of Elderly Drivers:</A> Yesterday's Young in Today's Traffic</STRONG> by J.P. Rothe

