</head>
<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<h2>DRIVER ED AND TECHNOLOGY</h2>
<p>
<b></b>
<p>Greg Adams, President, Interactive Communications Inc, told a recent conference of driver educators at Novi, Michigan that some developers of new instructional technologies are beginning to encounter resistance on the part of educators to their ideas.Adams believes that if driver educators are biased against new technologies and slow to embrace their potential for instruction, the public may not be; and maybe the instructional product will be sold directly to the public. (Undated, 1,400 words)

