<html><head>
<title>THE CHALLENGE OF ABS</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<h2>THE CHALLENGE OF ABS</h2>
<p>
<b></b>
<p>Some automobile advertisements seem to present the antilock braking system (ABS) as a sort of magic solution to the average driver's poor braking skills. But a recent report by the U.S. Highway Loss Data Institute, which represents insurance companies, stated that antilock systems aren't reducing either the frequency or the cost of crashes that result in insurance claims for vehicle damage. (Date: 1994;1,100 words)

<p><img align="middle" src="/icons/view-full.gif">
<a href="/pde/ARTICLES/free/abs-952033853.html"> VIEW FULL TEXT</a><p>
