<html><head>
<title>TRAFFIC SAFETY IN THE HEART OF RUSSIA</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<h2>TRAFFIC SAFETY IN THE HEART OF RUSSIA</h2>
<p>
<b>Reima Lehtimaki</b>
<p>Finnish traffic safety researcher Reima Lehtimaki and 
anthropologist Aune Kamarainen visited the Russion republic 
of Mari El (about 600 km east of Moscow) earlier this year. 
They have provided for the village a unique insight into the 
administration of driver licensing, driver training and 
education in this region. A short article is available in 
the News section of the Village. This article for subscribers
provides details of administration, training and licensing 
in the region.
