http://www.tsao.drivers.com:80/pde/ARTICLES/news/larson-96301-13300.html 206.51.17.124 19970119112902 text/html 4848
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 19 Jan 1997 11:28:56 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 4677
Last-modified: Mon, 28 Oct 1996 16:23:22 GMT
