<TITLE>International driver's license invaluable</TITLE>
</HEAD><BODY>
<A HREF="http://www.pde.drivers.com/pde/index.html">
<img src="/pde/home_btn.gif" 
     hspace=5
     align="middle" 
     alt="HOME">

VILLAGE Home Page
</A>
	<A HREF="/pde/infodbase.html">
	<img src="/pde/info.gif" 
hspace=5
		align="middle"
		alt="INFODATA">
