<OL><LI>Alcohol-impaired driving<LI>
Occupant protection<LI>
Speeding and speed limit enforcement<LI>
Older driver safety<LI>
Graduated licensing<LI>
Drugged driving<LI>
Highway signage<LI>
Automobile insurance<LI>
Motorcycle-helmet laws<LI>
Railroad-crossing safety.</OL> <P>

Other safety concerns prominently listed included: Department of Transport alcohol and drug tests for commercial-vehicle drivers, truck conspicuity, roadside inspections for commercial vehicles, driver fatigue, school bus violence, work zone safety, cellular phones, pedestrian safety, and the proper use of antilock brakes.<P>
