<TITLE>Task 1</TITLE> 
 </HEADER>
<BODY>
<img src="../gif/banner2.gif">

    
<h2>MEMBERS</h2>
<hr>
<h3>Contributing Members</h3>
Discussions are under way with a number of industries, municipalities, and other vested
    stakeholders for membership in the consortium. Contractual agreements have been completed with ProGold,
    <a href="acs.html">American Crystal Sugar Company</a>, Red River Resource Conservation & Development,
    Lake Agassiz Resource Conservation & Development, Pembina Trail Resource Conservation 
    & Development, Simplot Soilbuilders, <a href="http://www.simplot.com">J.R. Simplot Company</a>, Minn-Dak Farmers Cooperative, the city of Fargo, and the 
    city of<a href="http://www.rrv.net/GrandForks/">Grand Forks</a>. Verbal commitments have been received from several other municipalities, and additional
    participants are being solicited.<p><hr>
