<DOCHDR>
http://www.eerc.und.nodak.edu:80/9395bien/p106.htm 134.129.141.26 19970113180615 text/html 5471
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 18:10:08 GMT
