<DOCNO>WT24-B32-310</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA026-000279-B017-90</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.eerc.und.nodak.edu:80/9395bien/p227.htm 134.129.141.26 19970113182956 text/html 2974
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
