<DOCNO>WT24-B32-322</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA026-000279-B018-147</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.eerc.und.nodak.edu:80/9395bien/p255.htm 134.129.141.26 19970113183417 text/html 7767
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
