<DOCOLDNO>IA026-000279-B021-203</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.eerc.und.nodak.edu:80/9395bien/p314.htm 134.129.141.26 19970113184527 text/html 2646
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
